<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TSL_1000V Manual Gateway</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --tesla-blue: #0057ff;
            --danger-red: #d32f2f;
            --bg-dark: #121212;
            --card-bg: #1e1e1e;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 { margin: 10px 0; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--tesla-blue); }
        .header p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #aaa; }

        /* 安全警告弹窗 */
        #safety-modal {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        .modal-content {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            max-width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid var(--danger-red);
        }
        .btn-confirm {
            background: var(--danger-red);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* 列表设计 */
        .manual-list {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .manual-item {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--tesla-blue);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }
        .manual-item:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
        .lang-info h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem; }
        .lang-info span { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; }
        .download-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; }

        .footer { margin-top: auto; padding: 40px 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="safety-modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h2 style="color: var(--danger-red);">DANGER / 危险</h2>
            <p>本设备涉及 1000V 高压操作。请确认您已阅读安全规程并具备相关操作资质。</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888;">This device involves 1000V high-voltage operation. Please ensure you are a certified technician.</p>
            <button class="btn-confirm" onclick="closeModal()">我已确认 | I CONFIRM</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>TSL_1000V Discharger</h1>
        <p>User Interface & Operation Manuals</p>
    </div>

    <div class="manual-list">
        <a href="manual_cn_v1.9.pdf" class="manual-item">
            <div class="lang-info">
                <h3>简体中文 (Standard)</h3>
                <span>Version: V1.9_0206</span>
            </div>
            <div class="download-icon">🇨🇳</div>
        </a>

        <a href="manual_en_v1.9.pdf" class="manual-item">
            <div class="lang-info">
                <h3>English (International)</h3>
                <span>Version: V1.9_0206</span>
            </div>
            <div class="download-icon">🇺🇸</div>
        </a>

        <a href="manual_de_v1.8.pdf" class="manual-item">
            <div class="lang-info">
                <h3>Deutsch (Germany)</h3>
                <span>Version: V1.8_1215</span>
            </div>
            <div class="download-icon">🇩🇪</div>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        © 2024 TESLA HV Solutions | Support: support@example.com
    </div>

    <script>
        function closeModal() {
            document.getElementById('safety-modal').style.display = 'none';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
